    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "Pit- Playmar",
      "Cocktails\nUNITED'S VERY DRY BEEFEATER MARTINI\nUNITED'S VERY DRY SMIRNOFF SILVER VODKA MARTINI\nOLD FASHIONED\nMANHATTAN\nSCREWDRIVER\nBLOODY MARY\nMAI TAI\nDAIQUIRI\nWHISKEY SOUR\nSpirits\nI. W. HARPER BOURBON\nCUTTY SARK SCOTCH\nCHIVAS REGAL SCOTCH\nSEAGRAMS V.O.\nJACK DANIELS TENNESSEE WHISKEY\nBEEFEATER GIN\nSMIRNOFF VODKA\nBACARDI RUM\nCHRISTIAN BROTHERS BRANDY\n1.50\nWines and Beer\nCHAMPAGNE\nDRY SACK SHERRY\nRED WINE\nWHITE WINE\n1.00\nDOMESTIC BEER\n50\nCOMPLIMENTARY SOFT BEVERAGES\nMinors Will Not Be Served Liquor.\nTo Begin\nFRUIT CUP\nYour Choice of\nSPANISH OMELETTE\nGRILLED CANADIAN BACON\nHASH BROWNED POTATOES\nor\nFRENCH TOAST\nSYRUP\nGRILLED HAM STEAK\nBRIOCHE ROLL\nBUTTER PAT\nCOFFEE\nBeverages\nSANKA\nTEA\nMILK\nThis menu prepared in United Airlines Flight Kitchen\nat los Angeles Raoul Delhol Svecutive Chof\nMember, Societe Culinaire Philanthropique; Club Gastronomique\nProsner Montanne. Chevalier de Ordre de Saint Fortunat\nPlease accept our apology if your choice is not available.\nLAXHH\nR4.1"
    ],
